        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Hazardous Duty Pay for Frontline Federal Workers Act</b></p> <p>This bill temporarily entitles federal employees, including certain employees of the Veterans Health Administration and the Transportation Security Administration, who are exposed to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) during duty to a pay differential, as set by the Office of Personnel Management.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
